<p>
  <span class="nym">Malatesta</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>malus</i> 'bad, evil, wicked; ugly; unlucky' + <span class="lang">Italian</span> <i>testa</i> 'head'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The family name of the ruling house of Rimini from the late 13th to early 16th C.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


